                     <interp inst="t17761016-6-verdict40" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of 39 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron EYRE.</p>
